description: This file defines a data model for a national park adventure guide, sets up an agent with specific models, and runs an example to generate a park adventure response based on a randomly selected park from a list.

classes.name: NationalParkAdventure
classes.description: A Pydantic data model representing detailed information about a national park adventure, including attractions, trails, wildlife, and safety info.

methods.name: agent
methods.description: An instance of the Agent class configured with models and description for planning national park adventures.
